Flip or Flop Atlanta - Season 1, Episode 12




Small Budget, Big Kitchen

Ken and Anita get a lead on a 1950s brick ranch house in Ken's hometown of Marietta, Georgia. The margins are tight on this flip, so they need to balance inexpensive cosmetic fixes with big renovations in the kitchen and master suite. To sell this house for top dollar, Ken and Anita have to nail the rehab without going over their small renovation budget.




Original Air Date: 05-Oct-2017
